  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK36">
<l>aṉṟaṟivā meṉṉā taṟañceyka maṟṟatu</l>
<l>poṉṟuṅkāṟ poṉṟāt tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Don't say "we'll know it when we get there." Do dharma! and it</l>
<l>will be an undying aid even at time of death.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
